      <p>While your GroovePacker is being setup please take a look at these handy links and resources. For the most part you won't need a User Guide to start using GroovePacker but there are a few ideas about the flow of the app that once understood will help the rest fall into place.</p>
      <p>For example, GroovePacker recognizes products by SKU as orders import each day. It's always a good practice to import your products data first, before running your first order import. You'll find a video showing how in the Knowledge Base on our <a href="http://groovepacker.uservoice.com/" style="color:#66A909;">UserVoice page</a>.</p>
      <p>Other articles and videos covering setup and common topics can also be found in the Knowledge Base.</p>
      <p>Feature requests or bug reports can be submitted from the UserVoice page or you can click the small green icon which appears in the bottom right hand corner when you are logged in to GroovePacker.</p>
      <p>If you need support or have questions related to your account please email support@groovepacker.com</p>
